01:17:12.000 --> 01:17:18.000
but due to deepening of the functionality and expansion of powers,

01:17:18.000 --> 01:17:25.000
with adequate financial support.

01:17:26.000 --> 01:17:34.000
Also, I will talk about another problem of career planning,

01:17:34.000 --> 01:17:37.000
which is the lack of responsibility for employees.

01:17:37.000 --> 01:17:43.000
Here in the column we see that the responsibility of an employee lies in the plane of motivation,

01:17:43.000 --> 01:17:47.000
in the plane of updating his potential, both professional and managerial,

01:17:47.000 --> 01:17:51.000
and in his real and professional personal efforts,

01:17:52.000 --> 01:18:00.000
so that the employee overcomes obstacles in his professional development and in his managerial development.

01:18:00.000 --> 01:18:06.000
Here, as a rule, even the efforts of HR or external coaches are needed,

01:18:06.000 --> 01:18:13.000
coaching, as a deep consultation of an employee to reveal his personal potential,

01:18:13.000 --> 01:18:17.000
which is necessary for professional promotion.

01:18:17.000 --> 01:18:20.000
That is, it is the support of an employee in his professional growth.

01:18:20.000 --> 01:18:26.000
As we can see, most often now career growth, even managerial growth,

01:18:26.000 --> 01:18:30.000
it precedes personal growth of a person, personal development.

01:18:30.000 --> 01:18:35.000
And we see top managers at 23 years old, at 25 years old,

01:18:35.000 --> 01:18:39.000
and the social experience of an employee is not enough here

01:18:39.000 --> 01:18:44.000
so that he can effectively solve issues at such a high level.

01:18:44.000 --> 01:18:50.000
Accordingly, here, on the part of the company, there can be help in the form of consulting, in the form of coaching.

01:18:50.000 --> 01:18:58.000
And on the part of the company, the responsibility for the promotion of an employee is quality management of staff,

01:18:58.000 --> 01:19:06.000
it is adaptation, assessment, training, development, motivation and adoption of weighted personnel decisions.

01:19:06.000 --> 01:19:09.000
On the one hand, these decisions must be timely,

01:19:09.000 --> 01:19:14.000
they must be prepared by the logic of the employee, the logic of his development,

01:19:14.000 --> 01:19:17.000
the logic of his performance assessment,

01:19:17.000 --> 01:19:21.000
and they must be made on time,

01:19:21.000 --> 01:19:26.000
before the employee's ambitions go too far from the company's capabilities.

